arts.ttl: Copa del Rey round-up: Atletico Madrid win again, 9-man Getafe triumph as Leganes secure comeback victory
arts.sum: The last 16 stage of the 2024-25 Copa del Rey continued on Wednesday with four more ties: Atletico Madrid, Getafe and Leganes were all involved against lower-league opposition, while Barcelona hosted Real Betis in the only all-La Liga tie.
